# 📊 Ad Click Prediction System (CTR Prediction)

A Machine Learning system that predicts the **Click Through Rate (CTR)** of advertisements using user behavioral data.
The model estimates the **probability that a user will click an advertisement**.

This project demonstrates how machine learning can be used in **online advertising platforms** to rank ads based on predicted click probability.

---

# 📌 Project Overview

Online advertising platforms must decide **which ad to show to each user**.
This is done by predicting the probability that the user will click an ad.

The system:

1. Analyzes user behavior and demographic features
2. Predicts the probability of clicking an advertisement
3. Ranks ads based on predicted CTR

Example output:

```
Predicted CTR: 20.42%
```

This means the model estimates a **20.42% probability that the user will click the advertisement**.

---

