---

# 🧠 Machine Learning Approach

The pipeline for CTR prediction is:

```
Ad Dataset
     ↓
Data Preprocessing
     ↓
Feature Selection
     ↓
Train/Test Split
     ↓
Machine Learning Model
     ↓
CTR Probability Prediction
     ↓
Ad Ranking
```

---

# 🤖 Models Used

### 1️⃣ Logistic Regression (Baseline Model)

Used to estimate the probability of a user clicking an advertisement.

Advantages:

* Fast
* Interpretable
* Widely used in CTR prediction

### 2️⃣ XGBoost (Advanced Model)

Gradient boosting model used to improve prediction performance.

