---

# 📊 Dataset Features

The dataset contains user behavioral and demographic information.

| Feature                  | Description            |
| ------------------------ | ---------------------- |
| Daily Time Spent on Site | User engagement time   |
| Age                      | User age               |
| Area Income              | User income            |
| Daily Internet Usage     | Internet usage per day |
| Male                     | Gender indicator       |
| Clicked on Ad            | Target variable        |

Target variable:

```
Clicked on Ad
```

* **1 → User clicked the advertisement**
* **0 → User did not click the advertisement**

---

# 📈 Model Evaluation

The model performance is evaluated using:

### ROC-AUC Score

Example result:

```
ROC-AUC Score: 0.98
```

Interpretation:

| AUC Score | Model Performance |
| --------- | ----------------- |
| 0.5       | Random prediction |
| 0.7       | Good              |
| 0.8       | Strong            |
| 0.9+      | Excellent         |

